=============================
GNAThub 1.1 NEW FEATURES LIST
=============================

Copyright (C) 2014-2015, AdaCore

This file contains a list of new features introduced in GNAThub. A full
description of all GNAThub features can be found in the GNAThub documentation.

An ISO date (YYYY-MM-DD) appears in parentheses after the description line.
This date shows the implementation date of the feature.

New features in 1.1
-------------------

NF-11-O203-037 Display execution summary (2015-10-13)

  GNAThub now displays a execution summary once all plug-ins have been executed
  to spot failure more easily.

NF-11-O909-050 Support for cross toolchains (2015-09-29)

  GNAThub now supports cross toolchains defined in the project file as well as
  provides two new command line switches --target and --RTS to specify an
  alternate toolchain.

NF-11-O521-005 Support for SonarQube 5.x (2015-06-30)

  Sonar Ada Plugin now supports SonarQube versions from the 4.5.4 (LTS) to the
  5.1.1 (current stable).

NF-11-O115-012 GNATcoverage integration (2015-02-12)

  GNAThub is now able to parse GNATcoverage's reports and to import extracted
  violations to its database.
